Package: RuiCountMissing
Title: Function to Count Missing Values
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Rui", "Guo", , "ruig0401@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),)
Description: The goal of RuiCountMissing is to count missing values in a dataset,
    and this package only includes one function called 'count_all_missing_by_group', 
    which is to count missing values for all columns by group.
